lead_paragraph: Malaysia is considering halting the annual Formula One Grand Prix race after its contract ends in 2018 due to declining ticket sales and TV viewership.

headline.print_headline: Malaysia Mulls Scrapping Formula One Race Amid Falling Ticket Sales, Viewership
